1
00:00:00,477 --> 00:00:02,476
Love and hate are brought together.

2
00:00:02,477 --> 00:00:04,176
Through both reasoning and suspense.

3
00:00:04,177 --> 00:00:05,976
Travel mysteries are so popular,

4
00:00:05,977 --> 00:00:07,876
mystery churns in the ocean.

5
00:00:07,877 --> 00:00:09,576
He sees through the one and only truth.

6
00:00:09,577 --> 00:00:11,476
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

7
00:00:11,477 --> 00:00:13,877
His name is Detective Conan!

8
00:01:59,045 --> 00:02:01,444
You two should thank me.

9
00:02:01,445 --> 00:02:04,244
I've got a golden arm.

10
00:02:04,245 --> 00:02:06,244
Alright already.

11
00:02:06,245 --> 00:02:08,044
You're so persistent, dad.

12
00:02:08,045 --> 00:02:09,444
You know, Pops...

13
00:02:09,445 --> 00:02:11,044
You really are kind of talented.

14
00:02:11,045 --> 00:02:12,944
In lotteries, at least.

15
00:02:12,945 --> 00:02:14,844
I can't believe you won the first prize again

16
00:02:14,845 --> 00:02:16,644
which was this trip.

17
00:02:16,645 --> 00:02:18,444
What do you mean "kind of talented"?

18
00:02:18,445 --> 00:02:19,945
I'm a genius.

19
00:02:22,845 --> 00:02:25,244
What? You want to kill yourself?

20
00:02:25,245 --> 00:02:28,644
"Seiji Hario (30)" -Go ahead then, go on, I dare you.

21
00:02:28,645 --> 00:02:32,044
I've always done things this way, that's my style.

22
00:02:32,045 --> 00:02:35,045
I get rid of anything I don't like.

23
00:02:40,045 --> 00:02:42,144
Next stop, Shin-Shimonoseki.

24
00:02:42,145 --> 00:02:43,544
Shin-Shimonoseki.

25
